PREPARED STATEMENT OF REPRESENTATIVE MARK UDALL

Mr. Chairman, I move to strike the last word.
I  am  pleased  to  see  some  of  the  changes  included  in  this  amendment  regarding
the  evaluation  process  for  the  closures,  relocation,  or  consolidation  of  NOAA  facili-
