cility  will  be  closed,  relocated  or  consolidated.  This  covers  183  facilities  that  could
have  been  closed  without  Congressional  notification  under  the  original  definition  of
a facility as having a budget greater than $1 million.

I am also pleased that language has been included to evaluate National Weather
Services  field  offices  by  involving  a  similar  evaluation  process  used  in  the  National
Weather Modernization Act.

