Mr.  COSTELLO.  Mr.  Chairman,  I  ask  that  we  dispense  with  the

reading of the amendment.

Chairman BOEHLERT. Without objection, so ordered.
The  gentleman  is  recognized  for  five  minutes  to  explain  his

