which to submit supplemental, minority, or additional views on the
measure.  I  would  move  pursuant  to  Clause  1  of  Rule  22  of  the
Rules  of  the  House  of  Representatives  that  the  Committee  author-
izes the Chairman to offer such motions as may be necessary in the
House  to  adopt  and  pass  H.R.  50,  National  Oceanic  and  Atmos-
pheric  Administration  Act,  as  amended.  Without  objection,  so  or-
dered.

I want to thank everybody for participating and for your attend-

ance and indulgence.

This concludes our Committee markup.
[Whereupon, at 11:15 a.m., the Committee was adjourned.]

